WEBVTT

00:00.037 --> 00:02.171
Okay, so this is what
happened before on Star.

00:03.430 --> 00:06.054
You killed him!

00:06.056 --> 00:07.822
I met this girl on Instagram.

00:07.824 --> 00:08.990
They need a manager like me.

00:08.992 --> 00:10.062
Unless you get her hooked

00:10.064 --> 00:11.692
on drugs like you did Mary.

00:11.693 --> 00:13.361
Mama, we was just at the club.

00:13.363 --> 00:14.695
Stop lying, boy.

00:14.697 --> 00:16.831
Girl, Mama.

00:16.833 --> 00:18.899
There's a big music festival
coming here to Atlanta.

00:18.901 --> 00:21.836
You got to submit a demo,
and the deadline is in two days.

00:21.838 --> 00:23.070
If you want to manage us,

00:23.072 --> 00:23.950
show me the money.

00:23.952 --> 00:25.373
I need a job, I need something.

00:25.375 --> 00:26.741
You'll get haltonight,

00:26.743 --> 00:28.376
along with instructions.

00:28.378 --> 00:30.177
I do know you got to
tell them girls the truth

00:30.179 --> 00:31.012
about you and Mary.

00:31.014 --> 00:33.381
- I want Mama.
- Mama's dead.

00:33.383 --> 00:35.750
Simone, when
you gonna sing for us?

00:35.752 --> 00:39.487
♪ The joy I found... ♪

00:39.489 --> 00:40.988
Do something!

00:40.990 --> 00:42.957
Not again, God. Not again,
God. Not again.

00:45.962 --> 00:48.062
Lord, she's too young to go.

00:48.064 --> 00:49.997
She's just a baby.

00:49.999 --> 00:53.000
- Status?
- 16-year-old female,

00:53.002 --> 00:54.735
upon arrival was unresponsive

00:54.760 --> 00:57.523
to painful stimuli. Hypoxic, hypotensive.

00:57.548 --> 00:59.173
We just lost the pulse.

00:59.175 --> 01:00.674
One, two, three.

01:00.676 --> 01:02.543
Start CPR.

01:02.545 --> 01:04.512
You're gonna have to wait outside.

01:04.513 --> 01:07.748
You just... you go outside, okay?

01:07.750 --> 01:09.817
Pupils are reactive.

01:11.483 --> 01:13.327
Normal saline, wide open.

01:13.352 --> 01:15.434
Draw a rainbow.

01:16.659 --> 01:18.826
Let's prepare to intubate, people.

01:18.828 --> 01:21.495
Hold CPR. Check the rhythm.

01:21.497 --> 01:25.032
♪ There's a light... ♪

01:25.034 --> 01:27.535
Do we have a pulse?

01:27.537 --> 01:30.404
V-fib. Continue CPR.

01:30.406 --> 01:32.606
Shock at 200, please.

01:32.608 --> 01:33.941
Mama?

01:33.943 --> 01:37.144
♪ Inside the dark ♪

01:37.146 --> 01:41.682
♪ See the days are long
and cold and broken ♪

01:41.684 --> 01:44.552
♪ Filled with scars ♪

01:44.554 --> 01:48.456
♪ I know it ain't easy ♪

01:48.458 --> 01:50.791
♪ To keep movin' on ♪

01:50.793 --> 01:56.363
♪ So you can come on home to me ♪

01:56.365 --> 01:58.032
Clear.

01:59.769 --> 02:03.037
- ♪ Stay with me baby ♪
- ♪ Baby, baby ♪

02:03.039 --> 02:05.573
- ♪ I'm here for you ♪
- ♪ I'm here for you ♪

02:05.575 --> 02:10.411
♪ Through the rain and
the battles, whatever ♪

02:10.413 --> 02:13.247
♪ I'll be there, too ♪

02:13.249 --> 02:16.117
♪ 'Cause it ain't time to go,
yeah, this I know ♪

02:16.119 --> 02:17.685
♪ Yeah, this I know ♪

02:17.687 --> 02:20.054
- ♪ We got much more to do ♪
- ♪ Do ♪

02:20.056 --> 02:23.791
- ♪ So come on, come on back ♪
- ♪ Come, come back ♪

02:23.793 --> 02:25.759
♪ To me ♪

02:25.761 --> 02:27.695
Clear

02:27.697 --> 02:31.832
♪ I've been through it all,
battered and bruised ♪

02:31.834 --> 02:34.702
♪ This life... It ain't no way ♪

02:34.704 --> 02:37.104
♪ For no one to live ♪

02:37.106 --> 02:40.608
♪ My broken spirit's had enough ♪

02:40.610 --> 02:42.510
♪ I can't stay ♪

02:42.512 --> 02:45.946
♪ The system has failed,
I'm goin' through hell ♪

02:45.948 --> 02:49.650
♪ And I just want my
mother's love again ♪

02:49.652 --> 02:55.823
♪ Want to run into her arms ♪

02:57.860 --> 03:00.327
♪ Don't go, don't go, come on back ♪

03:00.329 --> 03:05.166
♪ Come on home, baby, back to me ♪

03:05.168 --> 03:07.568
♪ Don't leave 'cause I need you back ♪

03:07.570 --> 03:12.640
♪ Come and lay your head
down next to me ♪

03:12.642 --> 03:16.644
- ♪ Ooh, ooh-ooh, ooh-ooh ♪
- ♪ I know it ain't easy ♪

03:16.646 --> 03:19.847
♪ To keep movin' on so you can ♪

03:19.849 --> 03:25.186
♪ Come on home to me ♪

03:27.089 --> 03:29.423
♪ You don't have to stay ♪

03:29.425 --> 03:31.292
♪ Come take my hand ♪

03:31.294 --> 03:34.094
♪ You've had enough ♪

03:34.096 --> 03:39.200
♪ I'll wipe your tears
away with all of my love ♪

03:39.202 --> 03:41.669
- ♪ My love ♪
- STAR: ♪ So ♪

03:41.671 --> 03:44.872
- ♪ Come on back ♪
- ♪ Come on home ♪

03:44.874 --> 03:47.274
♪ Don't you leave, don't you go ♪

03:47.276 --> 03:50.811
- ♪ Come on, baby ♪
- ♪ I need you here ♪

03:50.813 --> 03:53.447
- ♪ Come to my arms, let me hold you ♪
- ♪ Don't leave me ♪

03:53.449 --> 03:56.083
- ♪ On my own ♪
- ♪ Just one time ♪

03:56.085 --> 03:58.118
♪ I want you home ♪

03:58.120 --> 04:02.356
♪ I need you close
right here in my arms ♪

04:02.358 --> 04:07.027
- ♪ So come on back ♪
